"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"# \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/g-ab-PFZHsTBNxslO1jDB.png?height=370&width=643)\\n\\n# Everyone wants to trade with coins, but they do not know how to do it or it is often difficult. SynFutures is an easy, intuitive and stable coin margin trading platform. ETH, BNB, MATIC, WBTC and other tokens can be used to trade futures and provide futures liquidity with commission income.\\n\\n!\\\\[Using margin tokens across chains can be an expensive and time-consuming process.\\nTypically, when using a trading platform to open a new position in a futures or pool, traders need to transfer the appropriate margin tokens (quote assets) to their account to ensure they have sufficient margin. \\n \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jZz7NJrmEv4ALAfBiw3W3.png?height=386&width=890)\\n\\nThis available margin allows traders to go to the “Trade” page and enter a trading pair before choosing whether to trade “Buy/Long” or “Sell/Short”.\\n\\nHowever, in order to prepare an appropriate margin token, traders usually have to go to a Dex or an exchange to swap tokens before returning to the desired platform, which is inconvenient and can result in high gas fees.\\n\\nSo SynFutures is introducing a unique native token margin function.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/HPWTR8PsGbfPKcq_-YIV7.png?height=415&width=700)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637125831,\"title\":\"SynFutures — Margin Trading\"},\"digest\":\"3HQindwtL3Mx6NltbEMgxYfUjaPxRnk0WYbiIp2a9tc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xAB451bFadADAe7b623469Ca2c0e9c3DEE1e779e7\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"_lpMQR-T4AqitYg95DWXkVzQGkCuQqWf58vndeQ1zZ8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vo4tyDKPP7wME9IVkxLUGcCiQWN1MiDnNsh0MietXkA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"XEeuAfilVOEJ7h91ItUMs6XMr-lyzVEp3eUfW0n5PU5nCvvGvZjY6DbTO_pJGd5Z9-GZkVNoc5rqzXO1nJgdvA\",\"signingKeySignatur